Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This meteor shower tonight's gonna be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this shower only happens\Nonce every 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A centennial celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We better get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, did you grab my quill and ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also packed a telescope,\Napples, bananas, fruit punch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...and my freshly baked home-made\Ntriple-decker nut-crazy vanilla cream cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again you read my mind, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is why you are my number one assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you are my number one assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed that! Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:00:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I said...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna bring the "Astronomical Astronomer's\NAlmanac to All Things Astronomy".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Astronomo-lomo homono what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that really old big blue book\Non stars, moons, planets, the Universe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's taking my number one assistant so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I put the astronomer's guide back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The book would have helped me identify\Ndifferent planets and stars tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Maybe someone borrowed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you don't need that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can already name\Nall the planets and stars, cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're super smart and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...astronomically awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Spike. You're such a flatterer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm a sweet talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And a number one assistant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Twilight! You're lucky\Nto have such a rad assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had someone to do whatever I told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Ooh! Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you want, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, pipsqueak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about taking out the trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, maâ€™am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have Spike to thank again\Nfor this amazing spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he simply amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I said come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Spikey-wikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew that big ferocious dragon\Nstarted off so cutesy wootsy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you are such a little star,\Nthat I had to make a little bow tie for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh. You guys are embarrassing me. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everypony! The show is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! These cookies are deeleesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, Spike, can you bring us some punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, poor little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww... He's worked himself to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the punch has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...spiked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams, number one assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Study of Comets."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Comets are small, irregularly shaped bodies..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"...that are made of non-volatile grains\Nand frozen gasses. They..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"...have body structures\Nthat are fragile and diverse..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... This is a job for Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If only he were awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for returning my scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo! Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, it's cold tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, would you like to relax in here\Nand keep me company while I work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo! Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. "...fragile and diverse with\Na surrounding cloud of material called a coma..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"...that grows in size and brightness\Nas the comet approaches the sun..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's already ten, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm scaly-tailed and bright-eyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...and ready to work twice as fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, don't be upset, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you want for breakfast? Oatmeal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a sunflower smoothie? Grass pancakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But my morning chores...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Owloysius did them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our new junior assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna help out with your chores\Nso you won't be so tired all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we need a junior assistant for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not tired. I do fine on my own.\NI don't need sleep, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, don't worry.\NHe's just here to help out a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I have to go out. So why don't you\Nintroduce yourself to Owloysius?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried? Do I look worried? I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, that's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Spike. I'm sure Twilight\Nhas told you all about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Spike? You know, assistant number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And who are you? And what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who?\N-Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your name was Owloysius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, "Who", "Owloysius", whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Spike, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! All you need to know\Nis that I'm number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you're number two. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a man of mystery, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm keeping my eye on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got eyes in the back\Nof my head too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That bird is out for my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove to Twilight that\NI deserve to be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Freaky Feathers over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him have my job\Nif it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a fantastical,\Nfluffelicious feathery little friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... HOOked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"He's just wonderful."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...the charmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Owloysius's just such a star...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...I just had to make this little bow for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he all saddle sore about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably just jealous of Owloysius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Spike feels threatened\Nor worried that Owloysius will replace him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Replace him? Hah! It's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike knows he can't be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to replace me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I better step it up and make sure\Nthat Twilight and Owloysius...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...know that I'm still number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike! Can you fetch me that book\Ncalled Two-headed Myth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mythological Mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Owloysius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Owloysius flew up and got the book for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and gee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I need Ferrets of Fairyland too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Climb down from there before you fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My last writing quill. It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Never fear, Spike, your\Nnumber one assistant, is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Quill... quill... Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Quill...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Quill, where is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I gonna get a quill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But the store is called "Quills and Sofas".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You only sell two things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Junior. All outta quills until Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Need sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore I had one here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A quince!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a quince. A quill!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. A quail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A quilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A quesadilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A quiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a quiche. A quill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Sorry. All outta quills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, chicky chicky chicky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, chick chick chick chicky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was calling out for you when you were\Nturning this place upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Owloysius gave me one of\Nhis feathers to use as a quill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...finish up the rest of my chores!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did Owloysius already do them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no no. There are quite a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine. Because I can just\Nstay up all night and finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's genuinely a good little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You said this book was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Owloysius found it right where it belongs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...but like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it get this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't wanna disappoint you and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen a dragon sneeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen a dragon lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very disappointed in you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You set me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, two can play that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "who"! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Owloysius is out to take my place. I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along, Opal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and get to Fluttershy's tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So lifelike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And when Twilight discovers it\Nshredded up on her floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...she'll think mouse-eating Owloysius is to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That poor little field mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Torn to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been Owloysius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, since owls eat, you know, mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible, terrible bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! I don't know what upsets me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That you deliberately tried to set up Owloysius...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...or that you actually thought\Nthis pathetic attempt would work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've let your jealousy get the best of you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is NOT the Spike I know and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't love me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold, hungry, tired and lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it get any worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is what running away is all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...I never wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gems! Mmm... Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if my tummy's full...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...the rest of me is still empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss Twilight and the pony gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But she doesn't love me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm better off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Seems to be getting warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The steam is great for my complexion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's sure getting hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU DOING IN MY CAVE?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,AND WHY ARE YOU EATING MY GEMS?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:16:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyah bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this was your cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't know these were your gems, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...we're cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... We're like brothers, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're a dragon, I'm a dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's us against the world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And your claws are super sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...extra spiky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't scare me! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to stay, but gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya! Wouldn't wanna be ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hop on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dark! I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo. Hoohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike. We were so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,*I* was so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you didn't love me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike. Sure, I was disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you are my number one assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that sometimes I need some help at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ask you to stay up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a baby dragon and you need your rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Owls are nocturnal. So I asked Owloysius to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But not to take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could ever replace you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even when you are being a jealous numskull.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never should have been so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry too, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been more sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And Owloysius...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know now that you weren't out to take my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Me. Forgive me, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He forgives you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How did you guys know where I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your ketchup covered feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Owloysius discovered your footprints and\Nwe followed them all the way to the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked pretty real though, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Princess Celestia will wanna\Nread about what happened today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready when you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike. Why don't you\Nwrite to Princess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And tell her what you've learned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that's a big responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing my number one assistant can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is Spike, writing to you\Nabout my adventures."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"This week I've learned that being jealous..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and telling lies gets you nowhere in friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"I also learned that there's plenty of love\Nfor every friend to share."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"So from here on out,\NI promise, that I, Spike, will..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who? Spike! You kno...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooooh...
